<div class="intro clearfix section__colorful hero">
  <div class="horizontally-aligned container vertically-aligned">
    <h1>I am Lily Nguyen, <span class="typed">a Bay Area based designer and developer.</span></h1>
    <button class="button switcher">And what else?</button>
  </div>
</div>
<%= partial "/layouts/partials/header" %>
<div id="projects" class="clearfix section__grey padding-large vertical-offset">
  <div class="container">  
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <% sitemap.where(:id.gte => 0).order_by(:id).all.each do |project| %>
        <div class="column-dt-6 column-12">
          <div class="work-card">
            <% link_to project.path do %>
              <div class="work-image" style="background-image: url('./<%= project.metadata[:page]["image"] %>')"></div>
            <% end %>
            <div class="work-section white-panel">
              <% link_to project.path do %>
                <h3 class="work-card-header">
                  <%= project.data["title"] %>
                </h3>
              <% end %>
              <p>
                <%= project.data["description"] %>
              </p>
              <div class="work-tags button-group">
                <% project.data["tags"].each do |tag| %>
                  <div class="button button-small <%= tag %>"><%= tag %></div>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="about" class="container padding-large section__white">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="column-12"> 
      <h2>About</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="column-12 column-dt-3">
      <div class="about-photo"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-body column-dt-9 column-12">
      <p>I am an interdisciplinary creative based in Berkeley, CA. I currently study computer science at UC Berkeley and am addicted to pushing pixels, crunching code, and delving into data.</p>

      <p>I currently lead design for Tequity and create interactives for The Daily Californian. Before that, I created products at <a href="http://scalablepress.com/">Scalable Press</a>, planned events at <a href="http://hackersatberkeley.com/">Hackers@Berkeley</a>, and wrote about startups for <a href="http://www.berkeleybyte.com/author/lilynguyen/">berkeleyByte</a>.</p>

      <p>When I'm not hacking, you might catch me exploring the Bay or watching a concert. Regrettably, I spend a disproportionate amount of my income on bubble tea.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
